  "text": "A little appendage to this. Do you use your vocabulary or the instrument's vocabulary to communicate with us? I am Ra. We use the vocabulary of the language with which you are familiar. This is not the instrument's vocabulary. However, this particular mind/body/spirit complex retains the use of a sufficiently large number of sound vibration complexes that the distinction is often without any importance.",
